_sText:
Beta Version of my previous map, gg_blubber_a1 About 3 more hours of work put into this one, but the results are much more pleasing. The map flows smoothly with 4v4, but supports up to 10v10. Total size of the map is 1.8mb, with the .nav I included it's about 2MB Any questions or comments just post, I'll get back to you ASAP.
Change-log - I removed 4 spawn points, so there are only 20 slots on this map now. This is to fix a spawn bug. - Changed around some textures, finally got around to painting alpha on my displacements. - Made my skybox smaller and touched it up a bit. - Changed around the lighting, I think this angle is much more aesthetically pleasing. - Also addressed the frame-rate problem.
This map is currently in circulation on the xF |:. Clan RPG Deathmatch server: 216.151.188.240:27019
